Package tud.tangram.svgplot.options Description

Options classes. SvgPlotOptions is used for command line options processing.

The other classes, inheriting from SvgOptions contain subsets of those options needed by each class in the tud.tangram.svgplot.svgcreator package. Thus the naming is parallel to the classes in the tud.tangram.svgplot.svgcreator package.
